text: The Alcalá de Henares Cathedral (also called as Cathedral of St Justus and St Pastor in Alcalá de Henares) () is a Catholic cathedral in Alcalá de Henares, Spain. It was declared Bien de Interés Cultural in 1904. Alcalá de Henares - Catedral Magistral de los Santos Justo y Pastor 4.jpg|Cover of the Cathedral. Fachada_Catedral_Magistral.JPG|Cathedral facade.
